Class RulesServiceBuilder

java.lang.Object
org.codehaus.mojo.versions.rule.RulesServiceBuilder
public class RulesServiceBuilder extends Object
Builder for creating a RuleService instance.

The builder allows configuring the source of rules (inline RuleSet, a URI, or a classpath resource), the server id for remote access, ignored versions and other optional runtime elements such as the Log and MavenSession.
